56
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:01,642
<i>...Important distinction.</i>

57
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:05,771
<i>This created brain is self-sustaining.</i>

58
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:10,366
<i>And it's capable of
emotional expressivity...</i>

59
