125
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:09,409
<i>No one has claimed responsibility...</i>

126
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:12,848
No, he's all right. He was very lucky.
The bullet only grazed him.

127
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:15,486
Yup. Okay. Take care.

