580
01:00:10,800 --> 01:00:12,768
It's extraordinary.

581
01:00:15,080 --> 01:00:17,287
<i>They'll be scared at first.</i>

582
01:00:17,440 --> 01:00:20,205
<i>But once they see
what the technology can do...</i>

583
01:00:20,360 --> 01:00:24,570
<i>I think that they will embrace it.
