596
01:01:41,880 --> 01:01:43,928
<i>These men should wait outside, Evelyn.</i>

597
01:01:44,120 --> 01:01:47,249
- Come on now.
- What are you doing to him?

598
01:01:47,440 --> 01:01:48,805
