659
01:11:12,960 --> 01:11:14,724
<i>So we did.</i>

660
01:11:15,720 --> 01:11:18,724
<i>Now they're all enhanced,
modified and networked.</i>

661
01:11:20,120 --> 01:11:23,567
<i>They remain autonomous,
