671
01:12:08,840 --> 01:12:10,171
Okay.

672
01:12:11,360 --> 01:12:13,488
- Bye.
- Bye.

673
01:12:56,920 --> 01:12:58,888
You think it's really him?

674
01:12:59,360 --> 01:13:01,806
