01:18:39,280 --> 01:18:41,806
<i>I don't understand, Evelyn.</i>

728
01:18:42,720 --> 01:18:45,121
<i>These are your dreams. This is our future.</i>

729
01:18:45,320 --> 01:18:47,766
No, this is not our future.

730
01:18:47,920 --> 01:18:51,163
